Group Details ::
----------------
$ groupadd devops
$ groupdel devops
$ getent group


Add User To a Particular Group :
--------------------------------
$ sudo usermod -aG group_name user_name 
$ sudo usermod -aG group1,group2,group3 username  //add a user to multiple group
$ sudo usermod -aG 

User Permission :
-----------------------
$ sudo chown azureuser file.txt		// change the owner of the file
$ sudo chgrp devops file.txt		// just to change the group
$ sudo chown azureuser:devops file.txt	// user and group both change
$ sudo chown -R azureuser:devops /opt/app // recursively apply to the files inside the dir


